attributes.title: Black Lives Matter ✊🏼✊🏽✊🏾✊🏿
attributes.review: I was courous and wanted to see what our president was up too but I nearly died! 😭 The army marched into my house with tear gas and said “VOTE FOR TRUMP 🍊🍊2020” 😫🥺 I was so scared.. So I look my black lives matter poster and they ran away in fear!🤫🤗 I was safe from the army but then in my sleep later that night the papers in my dream, They weren’t giving up and told me “If you don’t vote for Trump 🍊🍊 we will arrest you.” ☹️ O asked them why.❓ and they were dumfounded 🧐🧐 They realized that I had done nothing wrong and I had the right to vote for whom I wanted. 🤭😏😝 and if I didn’t want to vote for Trump 🤢🤮🍊🍊 Then I didn’t have too. So they did the unbelievable.. 😩😱 They tried to kidnap me!! And when that fails they then put me under custody.. “STOP RESISTING ARESST!” When I was complying! So I was sad 😔 and they help my hands behind my back and pushed me to the ground I couldn’t breath and passed out.. 😫😴😵😭. Once I woke up I was tied to a pole and an orange 🍊🍊 was standing before me! Oh wait it was Trump 🍊🍊😫 I was so scared that I was gonna die but then he said “ooOooOoO we’re gonna have fun” 🤢🤮 I was shocked.😫😦 I remembered that Trump 🍊🍊 was paedophile 😩😰 So I quickly kicked him in the shins and ran away! 🏃🏻‍♀️💨 On my way out of the building I went into a room with Barron and Melania locker in a cage they each begged me to help them. 🤭😬  As I used my 5-mintute crafts skills to unlock the cage Trump came! 😩🍊🍊😩🤭 So Barron using his height grabbed Trump’s head!🍊🍊🤕😃 But then his wig came off! So while Trump cried Barron, Melania and me all ran away! They ended up starting a new life in Europe and I went home to my family. THE END🙃😚😀👍🏼👏🏼
